The '''Grand Daern''' was the chief executive of the [[Marasan]] government, the [[Mindnet]]. Like all Marasans, the Grand Daern was a [[Cyborg/Legends|cyborg]] who could communicate with other Marasans through sophisticated computer implants. The Grand Daern's job was to collect data from the lesser elected officials, the [[Electnode]]s, swiftly process it, and make decisions accordingly. Due to the swift communication and computation allowed by Marasan computer implants, this system worked very efficiently.

Grand Daern [[Derra'makin]] was the last Marasan to hold the position before the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] conquest of [[Marasai]] and the [[Marasa Nebula/Legends|Marasa Nebula]]. He was forced to flee and hide on one of the colony worlds in the Nebula.

